{
  "id": "adv_event_2603_01_04",
  "title": "寄り添う\n想いを大切に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "私が原因で麻奈が落ち込むなんて……しかもクイズ？\nうーん……あ、もしかして優勝賞金100万円の？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 12.3283449173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.4798907991
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.5161678314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、思い出したみたいね。麻奈ちゃん、賞金を絶対\n手に入れて事務所の設備を一新するって張り切ってたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5161678314,
      "endTime": 23.2283449173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 24.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、番組の中でも張り切っていたわね\n100万円は渡さない、絶対負けない、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.416165924,
      "endTime": 33.401857757500004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 33.5896806716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "てっきり盛り上げるためだと思っていたから、私も\n思いっきり挑発しちゃって。まぁ面白くはなったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5896806716,
      "endTime": 41.7442839622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.32
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 41.9321068763
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "でも結果は莉央さんと同率一位で賞金は半額……それが\nよっぽど悔しかったみたいで、かなり落ち込んでいたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9321068763,
      "endTime": 52.234306049299995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 47.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんがあれだけ本気だったのは\n相手が莉央さんだからっていうのもあったのかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3987740516,
      "endTime": 61.075758171100006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.2654407183
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん……そ、そう……\nまぁ今となっては真実は分からないけれど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2654407183,
      "endTime": 69.1372776667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.3251005808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "私も、麻奈さんは莉央ちゃんを意識してたと思うよ\nだってリズノワのライブを初めて観た時に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3251005808,
      "endTime": 77.3058895747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.4937124888
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "心臓がきゅっとしてやる気がメラメラーってなってね\n絶対莉央ちゃんに負けないぞーって思えたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4937124888,
      "endTime": 86.5499933878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "絶対絶対、リズノワよりも沢山のお客さんを\n笑顔にしてやる～、って！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7378163019,
      "endTime": 93.233327357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.4316257158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、麻奈ちゃんってほんと負けず嫌いだものね\n自主練の時だって、同じ事務所の私すら意識してたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4316257158,
      "endTime": 102.81162563950001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.9982923824
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "「遙子ちゃんの笑顔はファンに安心感を与えてるよ」\nなんて、褒めてくれたと思ったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.9982923824,
      "endTime": 110.04829238239999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "「私も負けてられないぞー！」って燃え始めて\n夜遅くまで練習していたこともあったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2316257158,
      "endTime": 117.1155938783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "なんというか、意外ですわね\n私、麻奈様は完璧な存在だと思ってましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.0333287557,
      "endTime": 126.4316956838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.3316257158
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.6511499086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんの言う通り\n『アイドル長瀬麻奈』は完璧な存在よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6511499086,
      "endTime": 132.1511497179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.3511499086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "だって私達と同じように、不安や焦りを抱えていても\n絶対にその姿をファンには見せなかったんだもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3511499086,
      "endTime": 140.8955718675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.0844832419
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それってとっても苦しいことじゃないかな？\n完璧じゃないのに周りからはそう思われるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.0844832419,
      "endTime": 151.0515355108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.239358425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "私も、思ってもないことを期待されちゃって\nもやもやしたことがあるから、麻奈さんもきっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.239358425,
      "endTime": 159.62502698880002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.8128499029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そこが麻奈の強さじゃないかしら。さくらの言う通り\nきっと麻奈は誰よりもその苦しみを理解していたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.8128499029,
      "endTime": 168.6653439519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.8531668661
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……だからお姉ちゃんの作る歌は明るいだけ\nじゃなくて、寄り添うようなものが多かったのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.8531668661,
      "endTime": 178.1915112492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.3793341634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "苦しんでいる人を励ましてくれるような……\n優しい歌詞が多いのも、納得出来ます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.3793341634,
      "endTime": 186.5753207204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私も月ストを離れていた時、お姉ちゃんの歌を聴いて\n背中を押してもらっていましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
